OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784720909
OL,3,CTeenager sent England's Jess Carter
OL,4,Cracist messages during Euros, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FA teenager has appeared at court
OL,8,Faccused of sending racially abusive
OL,9,Fmessages to England defender Jess
OL,10,FCarter.
OL,12,FAaryan Agarwal, 19, allegedly sent the
OL,13,Ffootballer from Warwick racist
OL,14,Fmessages via Instagram on two
OL,15,Foccasions in July last year.
OL,17,FJess Carter represented the Lionesses
OL,18,Fin the World Cup Final in 2023 and won
OL,19,Fthe Euros in 2022 and 2025.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
