PN,34802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784720909
OL,3,CTeenager sent England's Jess Carter
OL,4,Cracist messages during Euros, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FAt a hearing at Colchester
OL,8,FMagistrates' Court today (July 21st),
OL,9,Fthe court was told the first message
OL,10,Fwas sent after England lost 2-1
OL,11,Fagainst France on July 5th.
OL,13,FA second message was sent on July
OL,14,F17th, 2025, when England beat Sweden
OL,15,Fin the quarter-final.
OL,17,FHe was arrested in September 2025
OL,18,Fafter the messages were reported,
OL,19,FEssex Police previously said.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
