CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784720909
OL,3,CTeenager sent England's Jess Carter
OL,4,Cracist messages during Euros, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FAgarwal, of Chigwell, is charged with
OL,8,Fa single count of sending a letter,
OL,9,Fcommunication, or article conveying an
OL,10,Findecent or offensive message.
OL,12,FHe is due to attend Chelmsford Crown
OL,13,FCourt on August 18th, when he is
OL,14,Fexpected to enter a plea.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/3
